an><span style="color: red; background-color: inherit;"><o p="" style="background-color: inherit;"></o></span></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; widows: 1;"><span style="color: red; font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">备注</span><span style="color: red; background-color: inherit;">2</span><span style="color: red; font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">：脚本中通过</span><span style="color: red; background-color: inherit;">scp</span><span style="color: red; font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">命令</span><b style="background-color: inherit;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">免密码</span></b><span style="color: red; font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">将备份文件上传到其他服务器，需要在两台服务器之间配置</span><span style="color: red; background-color: inherit;">ssh</span><span style="color: red; font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">互信。配置如下：</span><span style="color: red; background-color: inherit;"><o p="" style="background-color: inherit;"></o></span></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; widows: 1;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">在数据库服务器</span><span style="background-color: inherit;">oracle</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">用户上操作：</span><span style="background-color: inherit;"><o p="" style="background-color: inherit;"></o></span></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; widows: 1;"><span style="background-color: inherit;">[oracle@iZ94co90hfuZ ~]$ ssh-keygen&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; #</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">全部直接回车</span><span style="background-color: inherit;"><o p="" style="background-color: inherit;"></o></span></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; widows: 1;"><span style="background-color: inherit;">[oracle @iZ94co90hfuZ ~]$ cd ~/.ssh/<o p="" style="background-color: inherit;"></o></span></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; widows: 1;"><span style="background-color: inherit;">[oracle @iZ94co90hfuZ .ssh]$ ssh-copy-id -i id_rsa.pub&nbsp; oracle@192.168.4.78 &nbsp;#</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">用户名和服务器根据实际情况修改</span><span style="background-color: inherit;"><o p="" style="background-color: inherit;"></o></span></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; widows: 1;"><span style="background-color: inherit;">&nbsp;</span></p><h4 style="font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; widows: 1;"><a style="background-color: inherit;"><span style="background-color: inherit;">7. linux</span></a><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">配置</span><span style="background-color: inherit;">crontab</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">任务计划</span><span style="background-color: inherit;"><o p="" style="background-color: inherit;"></o></span></h4><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; widows: 1;"><span style="color: red; font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">注：需在</span><span style="color: red; background-color: inherit;">oracle</span><span style="color: red; font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">用户下通过</span><span style="color: red; background-color: inherit;">crontab –e</span><span style="color: red; font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">命令配置</span><span style="color: red; background-color: inherit;"><o p="" style="background-color: inherit;"></o></span></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; widows: 1;"><span style="background-color: inherit;">00 02 * * * /bin/sh /oracle/database/rman_backup/rman_back.sh &gt;&gt; /oracle/database/rman_backup/rman_back.log 2&gt;&amp;1 &amp;<o p="" style="background-color: inherit;"></o></span></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; widows: 1;"><span style="font-size: 14pt; background-color: inherit;"><o p="" style="background-color: inherit;">&nbsp;</o></span></p><h4 style="font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; widows: 1;"><a style="background-color: inherit;"><span style="background-color: inherit;">8. windows</span></a><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">环境注意事项</span><span style="background-color: inherit;"><o p="" style="background-color: inherit;"></o></span></h4><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; widows: 1; text-indent: 26.25pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">上面脚本只适用于</span><span style="background-color: inherit;">linux</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">环境，</span><span style="background-color: inherit;">windows</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">环境可以参考</span><span style="background-color: inherit;">linux</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">脚本自行编写批处理文件。</span><span style="background-color: inherit;"><o p="" style="background-color: inherit;"></o></span></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; widows: 1; text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="background-color: inherit;">&nbsp;Windows</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">环境不能通过</span><span style="background-color: inherit;">ssh-keygen</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">设置免密码登录，可以通过其他服务器共享目录，挂载到数据库服务器本地，备份时将备份文件直接生成到共享目录</span></p><h4 style="font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; widows: 1;"><a style="background-color: inherit;"><span style="background-color: inherit;">9. 关闭归档模式</span></a></h4><div style="font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; widows: 1;"><a style="background-color: inherit;"><span style="background-color: inherit;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial;">SQL&gt; shutdown immediate;&nbsp;</span></span></a></div><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; widows: 1;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial;">SQL&gt; startup mount;</span></p><div style="font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; widows: 1;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial;">SQL&gt;alter database noarchivelog;</span></div><div style="font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; widows: 1;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial;">SQL&gt; alter database open;</span></div><div style="font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; widows: 1;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial;">SQL&gt; archive log list;</span></div><h2 style="font-family: 微软雅黑; widows: 1;"><a style="background-color: inherit;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">备份方案二：</span><span style="background-color: inherit;">dataguard</span></a><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">灾备</span><span style="background-color: inherit;"><o p="" style="background-color: inherit;"></o></span></h2><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; widows: 1; text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="background-color: inherit;">Oracle DataGuard</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">是</span><span style="background-color: inherit;">Oracle</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">开发的一种数据库级别的</span><span style="background-color: inherit;">HA</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">方案，最主要功能是冗灾、数据保护、故障恢复等，它是生产数据库的</span><span style="background-color: inherit;">“</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">事务一致性镜像</span><span style="background-color: inherit;">”</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">，创建时，使用主数据库的物理镜像备份；创建完成后，备数据库会通过主数据库传输过来的归档日志自动维护备用数据库，将重做数据应用到备用数据库，以保证数据一致性。</span><span style="background-color: inherit;"><o p="" style="background-color: inherit;"></o></span></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; widows: 1;"><span style="background-color: inherit;">&nbsp;</span></p><h3 style="font-family: 微软雅黑; widows: 1;"><a style="background-color: inherit;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">一、</span><span style="background-color: inherit;">Dataguard</span></a><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">特点：</span><span style="background-color: inherit;"><o p="" style="background-color: inherit;"></o></span></h3><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 21pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; widows: 1; text-indent: -21pt;"><span style="font-family: wingdings; background-color: inherit;">l<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; background-color: inherit;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">一台主服务器，一台备服务器。</span><span style="background-color: inherit;"><o p="" style="background-color: inherit;"></o></span></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 21pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; widows: 1; text-indent: -21pt;"><span style="font-family: wingdings; background-color: inherit;">l<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; background-color: inherit;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">物理备库可实时查询，但是不能写入数据</span><span style="background-color: inherit;"><o p="" style="background-color: inherit;"></o></span></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 21pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; widows: 1; text-indent: -21pt;"><span style="font-family: wingdings; background-color: inherit;">l<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; background-color: inherit;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">更快速执行失败切换</span><span style="background-color: inherit;"><o p="" style="background-color: inherit;"></o></span></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 21pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; widows: 1; text-indent: -21pt;"><span style="font-family: wingdings; background-color: inherit;">l<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; background-color: inherit;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">可实现数据库读写分离</span><span style="background-color: inherit;"><o p="" style="background-color: inherit;"></o></span></p><h3 style="font-family: 微软雅黑; widows: 1;"><a style="background-color: inherit;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">二、</span><span style="background-color: inherit;">DataGuard</span></a><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">三种模式：</span><span style="background-color: inherit;"><o p="" style="background-color: inherit;"></o></span></h3><p align="left" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 21pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 15.75pt; widows: 1; text-indent: -21pt;"><span style="font-family: wingdings; background-color: inherit;">l<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; background-color: inherit;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">最大性能：可以使用任意一种传输方式，该模式下，一旦日志数据写到</span><span style="background-color: inherit;">primary</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">数据库的联机日志文件，事物即可提交，不必等到日志写到</span><span style="background-color: inherit;">standby</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">数据库，如果网络带宽充足，该模式类似最大可用模式</span><span style="background-color: inherit;"><o p="" style="background-color: inherit;"></o></span></p><p align="left" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 21pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 15.75pt; widows: 1; text-indent: -21pt;"><span style="font-family: wingdings; background-color: inherit;">l<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; background-color: inherit;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">最大保护：必须使用</span><span style="background-color: inherit;">LGWR</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">同步时方式，该模式下，日志数据必须同时写到</span><span style="background-color: inherit;">primary</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">数据库的练级日志文件和至少一个</span><span style="background-color: inherit;">standby</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">数据库日志文件，事务才能提交。可以确保数据零丢失，但是代价是</span><span style="background-color: inherit;">primary</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">数据库的可用性，一旦日志数据不能写到至少一个</span><span style="background-color: inherit;">standby</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">数据库的日志文件，</span><span style="background-color: inherit;">primary</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">数据库将会关闭。</span><span style="background-color: inherit;"><o p="" style="background-color: inherit;"></o></span></p><p align="left" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 21pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 15.75pt; widows: 1; text-indent: -21pt;"><span style="font-family: wingdings; background-color: inherit;">l<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; background-color: inherit;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">最大可用：必须使用</span><span style="background-color: inherit;">LGWR</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inherit;">同步时方式，该模式下，不牺牲</span><span style="background-color: inherit;">primary</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-color: inheri