    'title' => 'Redhat系统使用公网yum源',
    'tag' => 'yum,redhat',
    'summary' => '因Redhat系统商业的特殊性，刚装好的系统不能使用公网上的yum源来安装软件，下面就给出一种方法：1.安装epel软件（当前测试环境为rhel5.5）下载地址：https://fedoraprojec',
    'content' => '<p style="margin-top: 0px; font-family: verdana, SimSun, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">因Redhat系统商业的特殊性，刚装好的系统不能使用公网上的yum源来安装软件，下面就给出一种方法：</p><div yne-bulb-block="paragraph" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: verdana, SimSun, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.5;">1.安装epel软件（当前测试环境为rhel5.5）</div><div yne-bulb-block="paragraph" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: verdana, SimSun, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.5;">下载地址：<a href="https://fedoraproject.org/wiki/EPEL" style="color: rgb(2, 104, 205); text-decoration: none;">https://fedoraproject.org/wiki/EPEL</a></div><div yne-bulb-block="paragraph" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: verdana, SimSun, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.5;">[root@DCI yum.repos.d]# <span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">rpm -ivh epel-rpm-macros-5-5.noarch.rpm --force --nodeps</span></div><div yne-bulb-block="paragraph" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: verdana, SimSun, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.5;">2.备份系统自带yum源，下载公网可用yum源，并改名为系统自带文件名</div><div yne-bulb-block="paragraph" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: verdana, SimSun, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.5;">[root@DCI yum.repos.d]#wget <a href="http://docs.linuxtone.org/soft/lemp/CentOS-Base.repo" style="color: rgb(2, 104, 205); text-decoration: none;">http://docs.linuxtone.org/soft/lemp/CentOS-Base.repo</a></div><div yne-bulb-block="paragraph" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: verdana, SimSun, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.5;">[root@DCI yum.repos.d]# mv rhel-debuginfo.repo rhel-debuginfo.repo.bak &amp;&amp;  mv CentOS-Base.repo rhel-debuginfo.repo</div><div yne-bulb-block="paragraph" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: verdana, SimSun, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.5;">3.清除缓存，即可使用新yum源安装软件</div><div yne-bulb-block="paragraph" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: verdana, SimSun, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.5;">[root@DCI yum.repos.d]# yum makecache &amp;&amp; yum clean all</div><div yne-bulb-block="paragraph" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: verdana, SimSun, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.5;">4.大功告成，现在就可以正常安装软件了~</div><div yne-bulb-block="paragraph" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: verdana, SimSun, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.5;">&nbsp;[root@DCI yum.repos.d]#yum list</div>',
